source.name: Employment Plan Exempt List - Departments Under the President
source.description: Exhibit B of the Cook County Employment Plan, shows all Shakman Exempt positions for each department in the Offices Under the President. Department, Job Title, Job Code, Position ID and link to Job Description are included.
